description:
EndcProfilePredefined: Predefined profiles for 5G NR End-to-End (E2E) connection configurations.

- dateTime: Timestamp of profile data recording.
- Area_Name: Geographical area where the profile applies.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant Cell ID.
- Id3: Internal identifier for the profile.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- EndcProfilePredefined.endcProfilePredefinedId: Unique ID for this predefined profile.
- EndcProfilePredefined.meNbS1TermReqArpLev:  ARPU level for ME NB S1 termination requests.
- EndcProfilePredefined.reservedBy:  String identifying the entity reserving this profile.
- EndcProfilePredefined.splitNotAllowedUeArpLev: ARPU level where UE splitting is not allowed.
- EndcProfilePredefined.userLabelPredefined: User-friendly label for the profile.
